dcterms:description: CelebA-HQ contains high quality face images and is separated into two domains: male and female. Each category has 1000 testing images. The dataset is used for the Male→Female translation task.
dcterms:title: CelebA-HQ

dcterms:description: AFHQ consists of high-resolution animal face images including three domains: cat, dog, and wild, which has relatively large variations. Each domain has 500 testing images. The dataset is used for Cat→Dog and Wild→Dog translation tasks.
dcterms:title: AFHQ
